snippet.title: Johnny Depp Denies Fighting With Amber Heard Over His Altered Winona Ryder Tattoo
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Denies Fighting With Amber Heard Over His Altered Winona Ryder Tattoo..
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChjDtGelMNkllI5S22oO_aA?sub_confirmation=1
 The Mad Hatter of 'Alice in Wonderland' insists he never hit his former wife during a heated argument after the actress allegedly laughed at his 'Wino Forever' tattoo.   Jul 9, 2020   AceShowbiz - Johnny Depp has denied hitting his ex-wife Amber Heard after she "laughed" at one of his tattoos reading "Wino Forever" during a libel trial at London's High Court.    The actor is suing U.K. tabloid The Sun, its publisher, News Group Newspapers (NGN), and its executive editor, Dan Wootton, over a 2018 article which referred to him as a "wife-beater" in relation to domestic violence allegations made by Heard, which Depp has repeatedly denied.         On Wednesday (08Jul20), Depp entered the witness box for a second day, where he was cross-examined by The Sun's lawyer, Sasha Wass, who put to him Heard's allegations of domestic abuse.    The "Pirates of the Caribbean" star denied hitting the "Aquaman" actress, who he was married to from 2015 to 2017, on any occasion, including in 2013, when sh ...
